used by the men plotting the crime 
three men disguised as police agents entered lopez trujillos 
offices on wednesday and thursday asking for the prelate but he 
was not in said the church statement late thursday lopez is 
archbishop of medellin the countrys secondlargest city and 
chairman of colombias bishops conference 
