anatoly grishchenko 53 who has been hailed as a hero in the 
soviet union for his work to put a cement cap on the chernobyl 
reactor suffers from a preleukemia condition 
the lifegiving marrow from a donor in besancon france was 
carried in an ice cooler and rushed to fred hutchinson cancer 
