of graffiticovered concrete in front of the historic brandenburg 
gate 
crowds of tourists and souvenir peddlers watched as east german 
soldiers and west german construction workers with heavy tools 
began knocking away at the section ofwall that curves around the 
18thcentury gate 
the huge colonnaded gate represents the grandeur of old berlin 
just as the section of wall in front of it symbolized its division 
the wall provided some of the most memorable images of the 
revolution last autumn that ended four decades of communist 
oppression opened the wall and began the process of reunifying 
the two germanys with the giant gate as a backdrop protesters 
with chisels climbed on the wall last year to demonstrate their new 
freedom when east germanys borders were finally opened 
much of the surrounding sections of the 100mile wall already 
have been removed but the section in front of the gate is 
considered the sturdiest it is 10 feet high and equally as thick 
the area around the brandenburg gate has become a heavily 
visited tourist area makeshift souvenir stands hawk everything 
from postcards depicting the revolt to key chains made of wall 
fragments 
the work saturday was part of an ongoing process of removing 
certain sections of the wall the east german government says the 
entire wall will eventually be removed except for one section that 
will stand as a monument 
