german unification which would not radically tip the balance of 
military power 
shevardnadze insisted membership of a united germany in nato 
is unacceptable to us since it would mean a radical disruption of 
the current balance of forces in europe 
soviet and east german leaders also are likely to discuss 
polands demand that it be protected from any claim a united 
