while crews conducted inspections to ensure the safety of 
passengers said spokesman mike healy were in good shape he 
reported 
brad thomas a spokesman for pacific gas amp electric co 
reported that the quakes left 1300 homes in the concord area 
without power and scattered outages in other areas 
