cardinals said sportswriter brian martin 
people who have been through them knew what it was it was 
business as usual martin said 
at sixstory mount diablo hospital in concord nursing 
supervisor mary bacon said there was a sudden crack and then a 
rolling that goes on and on some of the patients and some of the 
employees were shook up and were sick to their stomachs 
the richter scale is a measure of ground motion as recorded on 
seismographs every increase of one number means a tenfold increase 
in magnitude 
an earthquake of 4 on the richter scale can cause moderate 
damage in the local area a 5 considerable damage a 7 reading is a 
major earthquake capable of widespread heavy damage 
