reservation the reservation home to some 14000 straddles the 
uscanada border 
the reservation was quiet friday and saturday authorities said 
authorities and mohawks had feared renewed violence when workers 
returned home for the weekend and casinos reopened although some 
casinos were open many of their employees stayed home and the 
usual busloads of customers were expected to be absent saturday 
night 
