brothels 
clients say the women charge 40 to 100 for their services the 
prostitutes wont discuss profits 
they say they have no pimps and keep all the money they get 
except for about 5 per customer they pay the bar for use of a room 
by contrast the legal minimum wage in mexico for unskilled 
workers is 390 a day mexican workers in some american factories 
along the border generally are considered wellpaid at about 100 a 
week 
the prostitutes shy away from discussing their personal lives 
rosalinda 26 said in her six months in acuna she has had sex 
with thousands of men 
her only complaints are slow nights early in the week and the 
american youths who come not for sex but to take advantage of 
mexicos lower drinking age 
you dont need them around rosalinda said in spanish 
what do you need them for 
